142
00:11:59,135 --> 00:12:01,596
There’s your orders, Major.

143
00:12:01,721 --> 00:12:03,765
See you on the plane.

144
00:12:08,019 --> 00:12:10,063
OK.

145
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:18,863
Kelly.

146
00:12:25,036 --> 00:12:28,498
