There’s the Inland Sea.

147
00:12:28,623 --> 00:12:33,169
Beautiful, ain’t it?
Sure is nice scenery out there.

148
00:12:34,170 --> 00:12:37,340
That’s Kobe over there.
See it, with all the docks?

149
00:12:37,465 --> 00:12:41,177
