197
00:16:05,548 --> 00:16:08,510
Well, we’ll talk about that later.

198
00:16:19,187 --> 00:16:22,524
Send Major Gruver’s luggage
up to his room, will you?

199
00:16:22,649 --> 00:16:24,484
