208
00:16:51,011 --> 00:16:53,054
Mark?

209
00:16:53,179 --> 00:16:54,806
Colonel Crawford.

210
00:16:54,931 --> 00:16:59,561
- Let’s get outta this clip joint.
- Just a minute, Captain Bailey.

211
00:16:59,686 --> 00:17:04,065
- What’s the trouble?
- I didn’t mean to bother you with this.

212
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:07,318
