strict orders against it.

219
00:17:32,761 --> 00:17:38,433
But when an officer
who should be an example...

220
00:17:38,558 --> 00:17:40,810
Am I to understand, sir,
that you personally

221
00:17:40,935 --> 00:17:44,481
