and I’m very embarrassed, but I’m sorry.

223
00:17:51,529 --> 00:17:54,115
- Thank you.
- Thank you, "sir."

224
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:58,286
Don’t you know there’s such a thing
as insolence through manner?

225
00:17:58,411 --> 00:18:00,455
